<item>
            <title>[SOLR-4716] this bug for fixed bug SOLR-4210. proxy request for remote core </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4716</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4210&quot; title=&quot;Requests to a Collection that does not exist on the receiving node should be proxied to a suitable node.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-4210&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-4210&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. remoteQuery() have some issue in tomcat. it&apos;s ok in jetty but not work in tomcat(maybe some other web server too) cause the IOUtils.closeQuietly(os) wouldn&apos;t flush before close . this lead a &quot;Bogus chunk size&quot; error cause the transfer-encoding is chunked and also the &quot;Content-Length&quot; was set to non &quot;-1&quot;. so we should invoke flush() explicitly before close.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
